OL,7,FExperts say food prices were the main
OL,8,Freason for the fall - with prices
OL,9,Frising less than they were a year ago,
OL,10,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,11,Fand Economics Editor Joel Hills report
OL,13,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt said he "would
OL,14,Flike to" cut taxes before a possible
OL,15,FOctober general election if he can do
OL,16,Fit in a "responsible way".
