OL,3,CHunt 'would like to' cut taxes before
OL,4,Celection if it can be done
OL,5,C'responsibly'
OL,7,F"But I would only do so in a way that
OL,8,Fis responsible and in the budget and
OL,9,Fthe autumn statement, I was able to
OL,10,Freduce taxes without increasing
OL,11,Fborrowing and without reducing the
OL,12,Fmoney available for public services.
OL,14,F"If it's possible to do more in that
OL,15,Fresponsible way, then yes, I would
OL,16,Flike to."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/19
