OL,5,C'responsibly'
OL,7,FWhen asked if he thinks he needs to
OL,8,Fchange his strategy to focus on public
OL,9,Fservices, Mr Hunt said he "wants to
OL,10,Fput more money" towards that too, "but
OL,11,Fthe way to do that is to grow the
OL,12,Feconomy".
OL,14,F"I don't accept that it's a choice
OL,15,Fbetween money for public services or
OL,16,Ftax cuts. The cuts in National
OL,17,FInsurance that I announced will mean
OL,18,F200,000 more people, or the equivalent
OL,19,Fof in-work that will fill around 1 in
OL,20,F5 vacancies across the economy.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/19
