OL,7,F"That is good for growth. That means
OL,8,Fmore money for the NHS, for the
OL,9,Fpolice, for teachers, for all our
OL,10,Fpublic services."
OL,12,FQuestioned by ITV News Business and
OL,13,FEconomics Editor Joel Hills over
OL,14,Fwhether he will try to cut taxes
OL,15,Fbefore the next election, Mr Hunt said
OL,16,Fhe "wants to bring down the tax burden"
OL,18,FThe comments come after the Office for
OL,19,FNational Statistics said UK has fallen
OL,20,Fto 3.2% in March from 3.4% in February.
