OL,7,F"We're actually pretty much on track
OL,8,Ffor where we thought we would be,"
OL,9,FGovernor of the Bank of England,
OL,10,FAndrew Bailey, said at an event in
OL,11,FWashington hosted by the Institute of
OL,12,FInternational Finance.
OL,14,F"I expect that next month's number
OL,15,Fwill show quite a strong drop," he
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FIn February, a 3.4% reading marked the
OL,19,Flowest since September 2021, when it
OL,20,Fwas 3.1% - but was slightly higher
OL,21,Fthan economists expected.
