OL,7,FFood prices drove the fall with prices
OL,8,Frising by less than they were a year
OL,9,Fago. Slowing price rises would help
OL,10,Fstruggling households who have faced
OL,11,Fsoaring costs in the last two years.
OL,13,FThe prime minister hailed Wednesday's
OL,14,Finflation figures, saying that after a
OL,15,F"tough couple of years" his economic
OL,16,F"plan is working".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/19
