OL,7,FHowever, financial markets pushed back
OL,8,Fexpectations for interest rate cuts
OL,9,Fafter the figures were shared amid
OL,10,Fconcerns over persistence in services
OL,11,Fand wage inflation.
OL,13,FEconomists had predicted a reading of
OL,14,F3.1% for the month. The drop was
OL,15,Fheavily linked to a slowdown in food
OL,16,Fprice inflation, which was also its
OL,17,Flowest for more than two years.
