OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News, Chancellor
OL,8,FJeremy Hunt said the numbers show the
OL,9,F"fundamentals for the British economy
OL,10,Fare very strong".
OL,12,FHe added that the public should feel
OL,13,Flike "we are turning a corner", but
OL,14,Fthat how "people feel is a subjective
OL,15,Fmeasure" and his job as chancellor is
OL,16,Fto focus on the "long term of the
OL,17,Feconomy".
