OL,7,FQuestioned over whether the public
OL,8,Fwill feel better off by the time of a
OL,9,Fpotential October general election, he
OL,10,Fadded he "hopes so".
OL,12,F"But of course, in an election it
OL,13,Fisn't just how you're feeling now,
OL,14,Fit's a choice about the future."
OL,16,F"I want to bring down the tax burden,"
OL,17,Fhe added, before clarifying he will
OL,18,Fonly do so in a way that's
OL,19,F"responsible".
