OL,7,FONS Chief Economist Grant Fitzner
OL,8,Fsaid: "Once again, food prices were
OL,9,Fthe main reason for the fall, with
OL,10,Fprices rising by less than we saw a
OL,11,Fyear ago.J"Similarly to last month, we
OL,12,Fsaw a partial offset from rising fuel
OL,13,Fprices."
OL,15,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,16,Fpointed out that inflation is still
OL,17,Fhigher than the Bank of England's
OL,18,Ftarget, adding: "Prices are still high
OL,19,Fin the shops, monthly mortgage bills
OL,20,Fare going up."
