OL,7,FShe continued: "The truth is Rishi
OL,8,FSunak is too weak to fix the economy
OL,9,Fhis party broke and too out of touch
OL,10,Fto deliver for working people. It's
OL,11,Ftime for change. Only Labour has a
OL,12,Flong-term plan to grow our economy,
OL,13,Fcut people's bills and make working
OL,14,Fpeople better off."
OL,16,FInflation for food and non-alcoholic
OL,17,Fdrinks dipped to 4% for the month,
OL,18,Ffrom 5% in February, to reach its
OL,19,Flowest level since November 2021.
