OL,7,FThe increased slowdown was partly
OL,8,Fdriven by a fall in meat prices and
OL,9,Flower rises for bread and cereals, the
OL,10,FONS said.
OL,12,FFurniture and household goods prices
OL,13,Falso contributed to the fall, with
OL,14,Fprices in the sector down 0.9% in
OL,15,FMarch compared with the same month
OL,16,Flast year.
