OL,7,FElsewhere in retail, clothing and
OL,8,Ffootwear inflation also slowed to 4%
OL,9,Ffor the month, from 5% in February,
OL,10,Fafter women's clothing stores
OL,11,Fincreased prices by less than normal
OL,12,Ffor this time of year.
OL,14,FThe largest upwards pressure came from
OL,15,Fmotor fuels, after the average price
OL,16,Fof petrol rose by 2.6p per litre
OL,17,Fbetween February and March 2024 to
OL,18,Fstand at 144.8 pence per litre,
OL,19,Faccording to the ONS.
