OL,7,FThe overall reduction in inflation
OL,8,Fcomes after rate setters at the Bank
OL,9,Fof England hiked interest rates to a
OL,10,F15-year-high of 5.25% in order to put
OL,11,Fpressure on demand.
OL,13,FEconomists expect inflation for April
OL,14,Fto show a further fall in inflation,
OL,15,Fsupported by another drop in energy
OL,16,Fprices, as CPI moves closer towards
OL,17,Fthe central Bank's 2% target rate.
