OL,7,FThis has also increased speculation
OL,8,Fthat the central bank could cut
OL,9,Finterest rates in the coming months,
OL,10,Falthough Governor Andrew Bailey and
OL,11,Fother members of the Bank's monetary
OL,12,Fpolicy committee have so far suggested
OL,13,Fit is too early for a cut.
OL,15,FIan Stewart, chief economist at
OL,16,FDeloitte, said: "Inflation is in
OL,17,Fretreat but the Bank of England cannot
OL,18,Fyet be sure that it is beaten.
