OL,7,F"Headline inflation is likely to drop
OL,8,Fbelow 2% in the coming months, but to
OL,9,Fbe confident it will stay there wage
OL,10,Fpressures need to ease.
OL,12,F"With earnings growing at close to 6%,
OL,13,Fand the economy reviving, the Bank
OL,14,Fwill be in no hurry to cut interest
OL,15,Frates."
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, official figures showed
OL,18,Fregular wages growth, excluding
OL,19,Fbonuses, at 6% in the three months to
OL,20,FFebruary, which was a slight fall but
OL,21,Falso above economist predictions.
