OL,7,FRishi Sunak told broadcasters: "Having
OL,8,Fbeen 11% when I became prime minister,
OL,9,Fit's now fallen to just over 3%, the
OL,10,Flowest level in two-and-a-half years.
OL,12,F"We have also seen energy bills
OL,13,Ffalling, mortgage rates falling and,
OL,14,Fjust this week, data showed people's
OL,15,Fwages have been rising faster than
OL,16,Finflation for nine months in a row."
OL,18,FHe added: "My simple message would be:
OL,19,Fif we stick to the plan, we can ensure
OL,20,Fthat everyone has a brighter future."
